.24, 211.3862, 211.9848, 212.5229, 214.3982, 213.7362, 213.4471, 212.469], "summary_html": "<h1>海通 高频量价因子在股票与期货中的表现 复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报核心论点：股票域的反转因子 (rskew, rkurt, downside vol, P-V corr) 在<strong>期货 T+0 + 双向 + 机构主导</strong>结构下翻转为<strong>动量信号</strong>。最佳期货因子：trend_strength (Sharpe 1.48), intraday_momentum 09:03 (Sharpe 1.97 — 但 paper 无费回测)。</p>\n<p>复现侧：8 因子全实现 + multiple blend variants。最佳 <strong><code>blend2_r10_h20_raw</code> Sharpe 1.123</strong> = -rkurt + oi_corr 等权 (10 日 smooth, 20 日 hold)。<strong>confirmed 报告期货 sign-flip thesis</strong>。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.58</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3447</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.6</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.35</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.52 / 0.67</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.06</td><td>0.69</td><td>1.45</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.01</span></td><td>1.5</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.64</span></td><td>1.09</td><td>0.08</td><td>1.68</td><td>0.68</td><td>0.09</td><td>0.46</td><td>1.21</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.16</span></td><td>1.13</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟级（聚合到日频输出）</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3936</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>96.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>34.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>8 因子（per sym, per day, intraday）：</p>\n<p>1. <strong>rskew</strong>: <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sqrt{N} \\cdot \\sum r_i^3 / RV^{1.5}</span>, sign + 2. <strong>rkurt</strong> (driver): <span class=\"math-tex\">N \\cdot \\sum r_i^4 / RV^2</span>, sign <strong>-</strong> 3. <strong>rskew_rkurt_combo</strong>: rank(rskew) + rank(-rkurt) 4. <strong>upmdn</strong>: <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sqrt{\\sum r_i^2 \\mathbf{1}(r_i&gt;0)} - \\sqrt{\\sum r_i^2 \\mathbf{1}(r_i&lt;0)}</span> 5. <strong>pv_corr</strong>: <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{corr}(P_i, V_i)</span> within day, sign + (long-R momentum) 6. <strong>oi_corr</strong> (driver, futures-specific): <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{corr}(P_i, OI_i)</span>, sign + 7. <strong>trend_strength</strong>: <span class=\"math-tex\">(P_n - P_1) / \\sum |dP|</span>, sign + 8. <strong>intraday_momentum</strong>: <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{09:03} / P_{open} - 1</span>, sign +</p>\n<p>R-day smoothing per sym, then cross-section rank.</p>\n<p>最佳 blend (winner):</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{blend2} = \\frac{1}{2}\\big(\\text{rank}(-\\text{rkurt}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{oi\\_corr})\\big)</div>\n<p>仓位：cr_rank → rank_to_continuous → vol_target_scale(0.15) → rebalance_hold(20) → T+1。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.54)</strong>: 8 因子 grid，R∈{1,5}, H∈{1,3,5,10}。R=1/H=1 变体 -3 Sharpe (4bps fee 全杀)。turnover 8.58。</li>\n<li><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.88)</strong>: drop R=1，扩 R∈{5,10,15}, H∈{5,10,15}。turnover 3.65 → gates pass。</li>\n<li><strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.93)</strong>: blend3 (rkurt + oi_corr + upmdn) + IC gates → turnover 1.00。</li>\n<li><strong>R4 (Sharpe 0.93)</strong>: blend4/blend5 + 加权变体 → underperform，4-5 因子组合稀释 alpha。</li>\n<li><strong>R5 (Sharpe 1.123)</strong>: <strong>blend2 (rkurt + oi_corr only) + 拓宽 H=20</strong> → 突破 1.12，gates pass → skip。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键洞察</strong>： 1. <strong>rkurt sign neg + oi_corr sign pos</strong> 双因子 blend 最强 (1.12 vs blend3 0.93) 2. <strong>2 因子 &gt; 3+ 因子</strong>：simpler is better; 4-5 因子加入弱信号反而稀释 3. <strong>H=20 (月频) &gt; H=10 (双周)</strong>：低换手解放 alpha 4. <strong>报告 thesis 验证</strong>: rkurt 期货 sign 翻转有效 (paper 描述与商品域匹配)</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：minute (<code>comm_data/1min/kline_all.parquet</code>)，需 close + volume + opi</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：80 商品期货</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：20 day rebalance</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：</li>\n</ul>  1. R/H grid 略缩，paper 最佳 (R=1/H=1 trend/momentum) 未还原 — 4bps fee 杀\n<p>2. intraday_momentum 单时点 (09:03) 3. blend2 是 rkurt + oi_corr，未含 trend/momentum 4. 与因子库 marginal corr 0.344 (接近 0.5 阈值但未达)</p>\n<p><strong>结论</strong>：通过入库，blend2 (-rkurt + oi_corr) 是商品域 microstructure 双因子，验证了报告\"股票反转→期货动量\"的核心论点。</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>R smoothing days</td><td>10</td><td>grid {5, 10, 15}</td></tr><tr><td>H hold days</td><td>20</td><td>grid {5, 10, 20}</td></tr><tr><td>target_vol</td><td>0.15</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>max_leverage</td><td>2.0</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ic_gate (weak factors)</td><td>252d</td><td>sym_rolling_ic_gate</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 6.19s</li>\n</ul>"}